nodes.title: how2use
widgets_values:
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  FAVICON / ICON Workflow                    │
│                                                             │
│  Very simple & fast workflow for clean, sharp favicons,     │
│  app icons, logos, UI symbols                               │
│                                                             │
│  Model used: uiIcons_V1.0 (or any good flat/icon model)     │
│     (https://civitai.com/models/327499/ui-icons)            │
│                                                             │
│  Current settings (changing may make results bad:           │
│  • Resolution: 256×256 (square, small & fast)               │
│  • Batch size: 12 (creates 12 variations at once)           │
│  • Steps: 16                                                │
│  • CFG: 5.3                                                 │
│  • Sampler: euler                                           │
│  • Scheduler: simple                                        │
│  • Denoise: 1.00                                            │
│                                                             │
│  How to use:                                                │
│  1.Change the text inside the [Brackets] to whatever you    │ 
│    want.                                                    │                                                             │                                                             │
│  2.After generation:                                        │
│     → Preview Image shows 12 different versions             │
│     → Pick the best one → right-click → Save Image          │
│                                                             │                                         
│                                                             │
│  Have fun making icons!                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
